Chet:<br><br>
I feel like I have been shouting and arguing loudly while someone's precious little girl is playing her first piano recital.<br><br>
You will be pleased to know that you advice has been heeded. Read some more... and learn that Doc Barry Spatz and I both are seeking common ground... a better position where we can agree to disagree.<br><br>
Some one called, Silent Warrior hit me between the eyes with a fear and ego cocktail.  I am reminded that &quot;He who exalteth himself shall be abased... he that humbleth himself shall be exalted.&quot;  I ran across another saying last night,&quot;A free society is one where it is safe to be unpopular!&quot; Adlai Stevenson.<br><br>
Doc Spatz and I can sit across the room from each other and silently flip each other off... better yet... maybe we can listen to the music.<br><br>
Thanks Chet, I will try to empty my garbage can at the dump and not in everyone's living room.<br><br>
By the way...the reason that you haven't heard from Doc Spatz lately is because I mailed him some &quot;Odor Eaters&quot; for his sandals.  Good Grief... I should have read the warning label!
